[[Translation:en/Community/NewGRF/Generic Road Vehicle and Tram Set]]
Generic road vehicles and [[en/Manual/Tramways]], for all [[en/Manual/Climates]]s, in [[en/Dual company colour]]s, with [[en/Articulated road vehicles|articulated vehicle]]s. This set uses [[en/Manual/Refit]]ting and generic cargo classes, so may be used with any [[en/New industries|new industry set]] (although some cargoes may use generic graphics).
[[File:en/Community/NewGRF/GRVTS preview 2.png|center]]
==Vehicles==
Buses:
*5x Normal
*4x Double-Decker
*3x Articulated (1 trailer)
*3x Express (coaches)
Heavy industry cargos (hopper, flatbed and tanker):
*4x Normal
*4x Articulated (1 trailer)
Light industry cargos (mail, box, armoured and refrigerated trucks):
*5x Normal
*3x Express
Passenger Trams:
*5x Normal (1, 2 or 3 car)
*3x Double decker (1 or 2 car)
Cargo trams (mail, goods, sweets and food only):
*4x Normal (1, 2, 3 or 4 car)
